rComments: I took his class my second semester of freshman year, and now I am about to graduate.  He remains the best teacher that I had all four years of college.  He was funny, smart and made the class interesting.  In the class discussions, there were always people fighting each other to get to speak.  I also loved the texts he picked out for us to read.

Easily my best teacher so far in college.  Very funny, easy going, but smart.  You know he understands what he's teaching, and he LIKES what he's teaching.  I'd take another class with him in a second.

He's the funniest teacher I've ever had, real down to earth, First teacher I've ever heard freely curse.  He was real cool when I kind of messed up and forgot that the take home final was due on a wed and not friday..
